│ Hello! As a senior LLVM maintainer for the `slp-vectorizer`, │
│ I'd be happy to help you diagnose this issue. Crashing in    │
│ the verifier after a pass has run is a classic sign of       │
│ incorrect IR generation, and your detailed report gives us a │
